-Wl*2- w(-2) - 2*w(-1) + 3 <= Tl -Tr <= Wr*2 + w(-2) + 2*w(-3) + 9

el                            em        er

initial state Wl = 3 Tl = 3 Wr = 0 Tr = 0

so it's -3<=3<=9


el - em <= 0
er - em >= 0

every time place w at left side with distance d

el - em decrease by (d+1) w  // more relax
er - em increase by dw    // less choice

every time place w at right side with distance d

el - em increase by dw // less choice
er - em decrease by (d+1)w // more relax

place w at -2, 
both side get more relax by w

place w at -3
right get more relax by w*2

place w at -1
left get more relax by w*2
